title: The B-52s - With The Wild Crowd! Live In Athens, GA - 2011 DVD9
description:
The B-52s performed their first ever gig on Valentine's Day in 1977. And 34 years later, in February 2011, they returned to their hometown of Athens, GA to celebrate with this brilliant live show. Wig-wearing, boa-draped, glitter-covered fans came from near and far to see the band deliver a sizzling set that turned Athens' Classic Center into a cosmic dancehall. A B-52s live show is always the best party in town, yet here in front of their home crowd they turned it up a notch higher. With The Wild Crow! - Live In Athens, GA is filled with all the excitement, fervor and energy of a classic B-52s dance party. Packed with all their fans' favorites, this show leaves no doubt as to why the B-52s are known as the World's Greatest Party Band!
